<subSubSection id="C30F6558FFF28222FC8DFEF7580B962C" pageId="18" pageNumber="1085" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BAA36D3FFF28222FC8DFEF7580B962C" blockId="18.[856,1504,160,520]" pageId="18" pageNumber="1085">
<bibRefCitation id="EF844B22FFF28222FC8DFEF75FA3957D" author="Bitter" box="[880,1016,323,345]" firstAuthor="Bitter" journalOrPublisher="Repertorium Specierum Novarum Regni Vegetabilis" pageId="18" pageNumber="1085" pagination="431 - 473" part="11" refId="ref27749" refString="Bitter, G. 1912 b. Solana nova vel minus cognita VI. Repertorium Specierum Novarum Regni Vegetabilis 11: 431 - 473." title="Solana nova vel minus cognita VI" type="journal article" year="1912" yearSuffix="b">Bitter (1912b</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="EF844B22FFF28222FBFFFEF75864957D" author="Bitter" box="[1026,1087,323,345]" firstAuthor="Bitter" journalOrPublisher="Repertorium Specierum Novarum Regni Vegetabilis" pageId="18" pageNumber="1085" pagination="481 - 491" part="11" refId="ref27774" refString="Bitter, G. 1913 a. Solana nova vel minus cognita VII. Repertorium Specierum Novarum Regni Vegetabilis 11: 481 - 491." title="Solana nova vel minus cognita VII" type="journal article" year="1913" yearSuffix="a">1913a</bibRefCitation>
) and later authors (
<bibRefCitation id="EF844B22FFF28222FAEDFEF759DF957D" author="Child" box="[1296,1412,323,345]" firstAuthor="Child" journalOrPublisher="Feddes Repertorium" pageId="18" pageNumber="1085" pagination="209 - 235" part="5 - 6" refId="ref28039" refString="Child, A. 1990. A synopsis of Solanum subgenus Potatoe (G. Don) D'Arcy (Tuberarium (Dun.) Bitter (s. l. )). Feddes Repertorium 5 - 6: 209 - 235." title="A synopsis of Solanum subgenus Potatoe (G. Don) D'Arcy (Tuberarium (Dun.) Bitter (s. l. ))" type="journal article" year="1990">Child 1990</bibRefCitation>
) include this species, implicitly, in sect. 
<taxonomicName id="4C154D50FFF28222FB61FED4597C9551" baseAuthorityName="Bitter" box="[1180,1319,352,373]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Solanaceae" genus="Solanum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Solanales" pageId="18" pageNumber="1086" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="section" section="Herpystichum">
<emphasis id="B961EAC1FFF28222FB61FED4597C9551" box="[1180,1319,352,373]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="1085">Herpystichum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, allying it closely to 
<taxonomicName id="4C154D50FFF28222FC8EFECA584395B6" authorityName="Bitter" authorityYear="2011" box="[883,1048,381,403]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Solanaceae" genus="Solanum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Solanales" pageId="18" pageNumber="1085" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="dalibardiforme">
<emphasis id="B961EAC1FFF28222FC8EFECA584395B6" box="[883,1048,381,403]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="1085">S. dalibardiforme</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, but its thickly coriaceous leaves and pseudostipules do not fit the concept of sect. 
<taxonomicName id="4C154D50FFF28222FADDFE2F59F09594" baseAuthorityName="Bitter" box="[1312,1451,411,432]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Solanaceae" genus="Solanum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Solanales" pageId="18" pageNumber="1086" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="section" section="Herpystichum">
<emphasis id="B961EAC1FFF28222FADDFE2F59F09594" box="[1312,1451,411,432]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="1085">Herpystichum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
presented here. Instead, based on morphological and molecular data (E. J. Tepe and L. Bohs, unpubl. data), it is a member of sect. 
<taxonomicName id="4C154D50FFF28222FC71FE47581F962C" baseAuthorityName="Bitter" box="[908,1092,499,520]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Solanaceae" genus="Anarrhichomenum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Solanales" pageId="18" pageNumber="1085" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B961EAC1FFF28222FC71FE47581F962C" box="[908,1092,499,520]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="1085">Anarrhichomenum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
